The following is the English translation of the results translated from Chinese:

1) The DMT of large-scale MIMO systems has been accurately expressed;  
2) Two low-complexity suboptimal schemes have been proposed;  
3) Simulation results indicate that the proposed two schemes exhibit good performance compared to existing schemes.

The experimental apparatus used in our experiment includes: 
- two scintillation counters S1 and S2; 
- three plastic scintillation detectors; 
- a set of collimators; 
- a natural tantalum foil target with a thickness of 0.1 mm, placed between the first pair of scintillation counters; 
- a trigger system composed of four scintillation counters T1-T4.
